ivities. These constituents work in synergy to provide the plant's healing potential, which has been studied and documented in various scientific research papers.", "properties": [], "properties_description": "The main therapeutic properties of Ruschia uncinella are antioxidant, anti-inflammatory, antimicrobial, and antifungal. The plant's antioxidant properties help protect cells from oxidative damage, reducing the risk of chronic diseases. Its anti-inflammatory properties, attributed to the presence of flavonoids and saponins, may alleviate symptoms of conditions such as arthritis and other inflammatory disorders. Antimicrobial properties, specifically due to the presence of volatile oils, enable the plant to inhibit the growth of pathogenic microorganisms, making it useful for wound healing and skin infections. Additionally, the plant's antifungal properties, contributed by the presence of phenolic compounds, allow it to combat fungal infections, providing relief from conditions like athlete's foot and other fungal-related issues.", "preparations": [{"name": "tincture", "mentions": 19, "confidence_score": 151, "total_score": 2869}, {"name": "infusion", "mentions": 17, "confidence_score": 141, "total_score": 2397}, {"name": "tea", "mentions": 17, "confidence_score": 128, "total_score": 2176}, {"name": "salve", "mentions": 19, "confidence_score": 108, "total_score": 2052}, {"name": "decoction", "mentions": 10, "confidence_score": 41, "total_score": 410}, {"name": "ointment", "mentions": 9, "confidence_score": 36, "total_score": 324}, {"name": "essential oil", "mentions": 7, "confidence_score": 26, "total_score": 182}, {"name": "infused oil", "mentions": 2, "confidence_score": 13, "total_score": 26}, {"name": "poultice", "mentions": 3, "confidence_score": 11, "total_score": 33}, {"name": "resin", "mentions": 1, "confidence_score": 10, "total_score": 10}, {"name": "extract", "mentions": 2, "confidence_score": 10, "total_score": 20}, {"name": "ruschia infusion", "ment